                     <interp inst="t18441125-53-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 464 yards of Orleans cloth, value 14<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18441125-name-389" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18441125-name-389" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18441125-name-389" type="age" value="SYDNEY AQUILLA"></interp>
