                        <interp inst="t18441125-name-393" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE DIXON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable</hi> E 137.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—the prisoner is the man, and that he had been before convicted of felony.</p>
